---
config:
  sequence: {}
  theme: base
---
%%{init: {'sequence': {'compactMode': true}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    actor User as Project Manager
    participant UI as Project <br/> Execution UI
    participant BFF as Web/Mobile BFF
    %%participant API@{ "type": "boundary", "alias": "Public API" }
    participant JOurney_ORCH@{ "type":"boundary", "alias":"Journey Orchestrator"}
    %%participant JO  as Journey Orchestrator
    participant IMS as Integration Adapter
    participant JIRA as JIRA Platform
    actor  JADMIN as JIRA Administrator
    participant KAFKA@{ "type": "queue", "alias": "Message Bus"}
    %%participant MB as Message Broker
    participant WBS as WBS Microservice
   participant DB_WBS_SCHEMA@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS WBS schema"}
   participant DBReadReplica@{ "type": "database", "alias": "Read Model"}
    
    %%participant ReadReplica   as DB Read Model
    participant NS as Notification<br/>Service

    User->>UI: Click "Create <br/>JIRA Space"
    UI->>BFF: HTTPS REST<br/>API POST REQUEST
    BFF->>JOurney_ORCH: Internal service call <br/>JSON request with <br/>project metadata
    activate JOurney_ORCH
    JOurney_ORCH->>IMS: HTTPS REST API<br/>JSON payload for <br/>JIRA space creation
    IMS->>JIRA: Authenticated <br/>REST API with JSON<br/>Create project <br/>space request
    JOurney_ORCH->>KAFKA: Publish event on <br/>message bus<br/>Topic: JIRA_SPACE_CREATION_REQUESTED
    KAFKA-->>NS: Consume event<br/>JIRA space <br/>creation requested
    NS-->>JADMIN: Notification of <br/>JIRA space creation request
    JIRA-->>JADMIN: Space creation <br/>notification / approval
    JADMIN->>JIRA: Approve space creation
    JIRA-->>IMS: Response<br/>JSON with jira br/>ProjectId
    IMS-->>JOurney_ORCH: Space created successfully</br/>:JSON
    JOurney_ORCH-->>BFF: Workflow <br/>completion response
    deactivate JOurney_ORCH
    BFF-->>UI: UI response<br/>JIRA space <br/>linked to EPMS

    Note over JIRA,IMS: Work items are created in JIRA during execution phase

    JIRA-->>IMS: Webhook trigger<br/>Issue created / updated <br/>/ deleted payload in JSON
    IMS->>IMS: Validate webhook <br/>signature, schema <br/>and deduplicate event
    IMS->>KAFKA: Publish event on <br/>message bus<br/>Topic: WBS_SYNC_EVENT
    KAFKA-->>WBS: Consume event<br/>:JSON
    WBS->>WBS: Transform issue type<br/>Epic->Milestone, Story->Activity, Task ->Task
    WBS->>DB_WBS_SCHEMA: Upsert WBS hierarchy 
    DB_WBS_SCHEMA->>DBReadReplica: Read synchronized<br/>WBS data

    alt Webhook missed or retry required
        WBS->>IMS: REST API call<br/>Request incremental <br/>reconciliation.
        IMS->>JIRA: Authenticated REST API<br/>GET changed issues <br/>since last sync in JSON
        JIRA-->>IMS: JSON response with <br/>changed <br/>issues batch
        IMS->>KAFKA: Publish reconciliation <br/>events on message bus
        KAFKA-->>WBS: Consume <br/>reconciliation <br/>events
        WBS->>DB_WBS_SCHEMA: Upsert missing <br/>corrected <br/>WBS records
    end